    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty. It's honestly in pristine condition\u2014looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner so happy! Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
