    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is an absolute gem and looks just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been pampered, garage-kept, and is in truly flawless shape inside and out. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or speck of dust here\u2014it\u2019s basically brand new. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved to perfection, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
      "price": 43500.0,
